        <item>
            <title>《刺客教條：暗影者》開放預購，登上 PS5、PC、Xbox X/S 等平台</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/24/assassins-creed-shadows-3/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=assassins-creed-shadows-3</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/24/assassins-creed-shadows-3/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 06:30:54 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Assassin's Creed Shadows]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1288597</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Ubisoft 宣佈《刺客教條》系列全新作品《刺客教條：暗影者》現已開放預購，並將於 3 月 20 日全球同步推出。預購玩家將可免費獲得「淡路獵爪」擴充內容，該內容包含新地區、新技能以及超過 10 小時的額外遊戲時間。遊戲將登陸 PlayStation 5、Xbox Series X|S、配備 Apple 晶片的 Mac（Mac App Store）、Windows PC（包括 Ubisoft Store、Steam、Epic Games Store）和 Amazon Luna 平台。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1288617 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_embargo_keyart_-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_embargo_keyart_-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_embargo_keyart_.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_embargo_keyart_-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1288601" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_147_screenshot_-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_147_screenshot_-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_147_screenshot_.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1288602 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_149_screenshot_-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_149_screenshot_-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_149_screenshot_.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>穿越至 16 世紀日本的史詩冒險</h2><p>由 Ubisoft 魁北克工作室主導開發的《刺客教條：暗影者》，將玩家帶入 16 世紀的日本，探索忍術專家伊賀女刺客奈緒江和傳奇武士彌助之間錯綜複雜的故事。在這片動盪的土地上，兩位主角將在日本統一的歷史進程中與大名織田信長的野心正面交鋒。遊戲的劇情預告片揭示了兩人如何在內憂外患的背景下，共同開創新教條的未來。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1288600" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_113_screenshot_-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_113_screenshot_-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_113_screenshot_.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1288604" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_164_screenshot_-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_164_screenshot_-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_164_screenshot_.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1288605" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_165_screenshot_-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_165_screenshot_-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_165_screenshot_.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1288606" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_166_screenshot_-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_166_screenshot_-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_166_screenshot_.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>多版本選擇與專屬內容</h2><p>《刺客教條：暗影者》將推出標準版、數碼豪華版及典藏版，滿足不同玩家需求：</p><ul><li><strong>數碼豪華版</strong>：包含遊戲主程式、「赤龍雙組合包」（包括奈緒江和彌助的專屬裝備與武器）、「赤龍藏身處組合包」（提供藏身處外觀）以及「精通點數」。</li><li><strong>典藏版</strong>：除豪華版數碼內容外，還包括實體收藏品，如 Steelbook 鐵盒、世界地圖、奈緒江與彌助公仔、武士刀刀鐔、壁掛教條卷軸、76 頁藝術圖集及兩幅水墨畫印刷作品。</li></ul><h2>預購福利：免費擴充內容與專屬任務</h2><p>預購任何版本的玩家將可免費獲得將於 2025 年稍後推出的「淡路獵爪」擴充內容。這項 DLC 增加全新開放區域，帶來更多遊戲時間、新技能和裝備。奈緒江更將獲得新武器「棒」（Bō），協助對抗淡路島上的危險勢力「山賊派」。此外，預購玩家還可解鎖專屬任務「狗命坎坷」，該任務將於遊戲發售時提供。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1288607" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_172_screenshot_-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_172_screenshot_-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_172_screenshot_.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1288608" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_181_screenshot_-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_181_screenshot_-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_181_screenshot_.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1288609" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_coa_naoe_kick_t-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_coa_naoe_kick_t-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_coa_naoe_kick_t.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1288610" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_coa_naoe_kick_t-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_coa_naoe_kick_t-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_coa_naoe_kick_t-1.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1288611" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_coa_vista-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_coa_vista-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_coa_vista.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/01/24/assassins-creed-shadows-3/game-channel/">《刺客教條：暗影者》開放預購，登上 PS5、PC、Xbox X/S 等平台</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
