        <item>
            <title>2025 年袖珍相機歸位！  Panasonic LUMIX DC-TZ99 具 30 倍光學變焦</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/24/panasonic-lumix-dc-tz99/dc/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=panasonic-lumix-dc-tz99</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/24/panasonic-lumix-dc-tz99/dc/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 05:34:53 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[數碼相機]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Panasonic LUMIX DC-TZ99]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[袖珍相機]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1288587</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Panasonic 推出全新 LUMIX DC-TZ99 袖珍便攜相機，具備 24-720mm LEICA DC 鏡頭和 30 倍光學變焦功能。這款小型相機專為追求高質感影像的用家設計，無論是捕捉遙遠風景還是近距離特寫，都能呈現清晰細緻的畫面。同時相機內置五軸混合 OIS+ 防震功能，即使在全變焦模式下也能穩定拍攝，適合熱愛旅行和日常攝影的消費者。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1288592 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/tz99_k_slanton-694x520.png" alt="" width="694" height="520" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/tz99_k_slanton-694x520.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/tz99_k_slanton.png 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1288593 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/tz99_s_slanton-694x520.png" alt="" width="694" height="520" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/tz99_s_slanton-694x520.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/tz99_s_slanton.png 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Panasonic LUMIX DC-TZ99 支援 4K 影片拍攝，可錄製高達 30p 的高品質影像，同時提供每秒 30 張的快速 4K 連拍功能，確保精彩瞬間不被錯過。除此之外，相機還具備 120 fps 高速錄影功能，讓用家輕鬆創作出慢動作鏡頭，增添影像的創意空間。</p><p>這款相機針對旅行需求進行優化，內建 1,840,000 點可傾斜觸控屏幕，用家可輕鬆調整拍攝角度；同時配備 USB Type-C 接口，隨時為相機充電，確保電量充足。內建藍牙 v5.0 和 Wi-Fi 功能，結合專用的「傳送影像」按鈕，讓用家能快速將相片傳輸到智能手機，輕鬆分享每個瞬間。</p><h3>型號與售價</h3><ul><li><strong>DC-TZ99</strong>：HK$3,990</li></ul><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/01/24/panasonic-lumix-dc-tz99/dc/">2025 年袖珍相機歸位！  Panasonic LUMIX DC-TZ99 具 30 倍光學變焦</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
